Paper: hep-th/9605055

Date: 1996-05-08

Title: Half-whole Dimensions in Quaternionic Quantum Mechanics

Authors: De Leo Stefano (Dip. di Fisica, INFN, Lecce)

Comments: 9 pages, Revtex, Prog. Theor. Phys. (to be published)

Journal-ref: Prog.Theor.Phys. 95 (1996) 1029-1040

We introduce {\em half-whole} dimensions for quaternionic matrices andpropose a quaternionic version of the Frobenius-Schur theorem which allows usto obtain the proper quaternionic dimensionality for the representations of theDirac and Duffin-Kemmer-Petiau (DKP) algebras.